{{#> base title="Account Created" header="Welcome to AutoCare!"}}
  <h2>Hello {{name}},</h2>
  <p>Thank you for creating an account with AutoCare! We're excited to have you join our network of vehicle owners and service providers.</p>

  <div class="highlight-box">
    <p><strong>Account Details:</strong></p>
    <p><strong>Email:</strong> {{email}}</p>
    {{#if username}}<p><strong>Username:</strong> {{username}}</p>{{/if}}
    {{#if password}}<p><strong>Password:</strong> {{password}}</p>{{/if}}
    <p>For security reasons, we recommend changing your password after first login. If you need to reset it, you can use our password reset feature.</p>
  </div>

  <p>With your AutoCare account, you can:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Book vehicle maintenance and repair services</li>
    <li>Schedule regular servicing appointments</li>
    <li>Access pickup and drop-off services</li>
    <li>Track your vehicle's service history</li>
    <li>Receive service reminders and updates</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="text-center">
    <a href="{{websiteUrl}}" class="button">Get Started Now</a>
  </div>

  <div class="alert-box">
    <p>If you did not create this account or have any questions, please contact our support team immediately at {{supportEmail}}.</p>
  </div>
{{/base}}
